The '''Tortoise''' (''Testudines giganteus'') are trained tortoises used by the [[Gnome]]s in battle. They can be found north-west of the [[Grand Tree]] in the [[Tree Gnome Stronghold]], just north of the swamp. [[Trainer Nacklepen]] is in charge of their combat development.

